 that what I say is true.  Then you can come back here and apologize to me, but please learn how to use punctuation marks by then.</p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Duke Ardnahoy<br>Noble Lord Protector of the 70th Crusade<br>Fennin Ro - EQ I<br><br>Ardnahoy<br>Gimp Newb Tank<br>Mistmore - EQ II</td></tr>
